{
  "chapter": 124,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲和徐子陵在襄阳城外遇到沙福，得知少夫人的儿子小公子病重，二人假扮大夫莫为和莫一心登船诊治。在船上遇到护院马许然和陈来满，马许然态度傲慢，陈来满则较为友善。徐子陵诊断小公子中了热毒，与寇仲联手用长生诀真气驱毒成功。小公子醒后指认侍婢小珠用针刺他，小珠露出凶光逃走，马许然暗中助其逃脱。寇仲揭露马许然的行为，双方对峙。马许然假装无辜，少夫人无法决断，寇仲出手制服马许然。此时襄阳城传来喊叫声，众人愕然。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "仆人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请问两位是不是懂得治病的呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是甚么事呢，我们是懂得点医术的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫沙福，若老先生懂得治病，请随我来，我们定不会薄待先生。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "引路吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们本以为到襄阳便可找到大夫，那知却不准入城，幸好见到两位背着山草药囊，故试问一声，岂知真碰对了，两位高姓大名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫莫为，他是我侄儿兼徒儿莫一心，专以推拿穴位配药治病，包医奇难杂症，手到病除。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就好了，我家小公子不知如何忽然阵寒阵热，神智不清。唉！少夫人这么好心肠的人，却偏要受到这种折磨。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "船上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大夫到了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_xu_ran",
      "speaker_name": "马许然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位兄台须先留下佩刀，才可入舱为公子诊治。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "规矩是死的，两位朋友请进来，少夫人等得急呢！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下陈来满，不知老丈和这位仁兄如何称呼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫莫为，这是老夫的徒儿兼侄儿莫一心。救人如救火，可否立即领老夫去见小公子？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位请随陈某来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小凤，告诉少夫人，大夫来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大夫请进，少夫人等得心焦了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_fu",
      "speaker_name": "沙福",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和马老师在外边等候吧！莫大夫请进！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少夫人！大夫请来了。这位是莫大夫，这另一位是莫大夫的徒儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麻烦两位先生，小儿…唉…",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请问小公子如何发病的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今早起来，小珠侍候进儿时，进儿就是这样子呢！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫大夫请过来，不用拘礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小公子是中了毒！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人小心！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎会是这样呢？莫大夫有办法救他吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少夫人放心，家叔乃行走江湖，尝尽百草的妙手神医，必可…嘿…",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫大夫有多少成把握？我也曾为小公子探脉，他确是经脉紊乱，急促疲弱，但看气色却没有丝毫中毒的现象。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是一种奇怪的热毒，深藏脏腑之内，破坏小公子的生机，老夫有十成把握可断实情如此。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大夫能治好他吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一心！你给我按着小公子的天灵穴。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫大夫懂得运气躯毒之法吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是传自先祖的家传躯毒大法，能根除任何奇毒，陈老师请忍耐片刻，便知究竟。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是谁下的毒呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_lai_man",
      "speaker_name": "陈来满",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来满办事不力，请少夫人降罪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁都料不到会有这种事情，责不在陈老师，何罪之有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马老师刚才暗助小珠逃走，却又该当何罪？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_xu_ran",
      "speaker_name": "马许然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这两句话是甚么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明人不作暗事，只有卑鄙之徒才会扮作明是出手，暗中却在放那害人精逃走，马老师该知江湖规矩，有胆子做这种事便该有胆子承认。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_xu_ran",
      "speaker_name": "马许然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的规矩却是出口伤人者死，胡言乱语者必惹大祸，待我看看你这两个江湖郎中有甚么斤两。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_xu_ran",
      "speaker_name": "马许然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "许然清清白白，请少夫人为许然作主。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事那到妇道人家来管呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快将马老师扎个结实，再严刑侍候，保证可查出谁在背后指使。哼！真窝囊。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 124,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    }
  ],
